      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"1. ROCKET SUSIE drew the inside and won last time at this track and distance (17.69) after leading through, scoring by 4.5 lengths. Draws the rails again and looks the one to beat. 8. ROUGH GIRL MEL comes off an average run last start when fifth at this track over 305m behind Rough Girl Slim (18.13) in a Other. Placed at her previous run. Better than last start and can bounce back. 2. CADILLAC MAGIC put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Rough Boy Rocky (17.89) in a Grade 6. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Will give a great sight again. 4. LUST TO BURN was out of the money here last time out but can bounce back.\",\"runners\":[1,8,2,4],\"exclusive\":false}",
